solutions.title: BiomarkerNavigator
solutions.description: The Biomarkers Navigator One stop shop for biomarker analysis. Center of knowledge which facilitates the sharing of clinical Biomarker insights throughout the organization. Streamlines multiple approaches for time-to-Event Analysis, reducing workload for bioinformatics teams. Accelerates knowledge retrieval for stakeholders.

solutions.title: Population Models
solutions.description: This application provides real-time data-driven insights to identify trial designs likely to outperform standard of care (SoC) by integrating evidence across real-world data (RWD), AstraZeneca and competitor clinical trials

solutions.title: DominoData RAG KnowledgeBase Manager
solutions.description: Enterprise-grade knowledge base management system for RAG applications. Features comprehensive document processing, metadata management, and embedding generation. Supports multiple file formats, Azure OpenAI integration, and includes built-in privacy controls and compliance with AZ AI governance framework.
